Freeadvice is an affiliate of the [[Advice Company]] located in [[Sausalito, California]]<ref>{{cite web|title=About FreeAdvice.com|url=http://www.freeadvice.com/company/aboutus.htm|website=FreeAdvice.com|publisher=Advice Company|accessdate=29 August 2016}}</ref> and was founded by attorney Gerry Goldsholle.<ref>{{cite web|title=FreeAdvice.com Press Release|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20050322005942/en/Free-Living-Form-FreeAdvice.com|website=Business Wire|publisher=Business Wire|accessdate=29 August 2016}}</ref>

